Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.33,0:01:50.58,Default,,0,0,0,,HYUNCKEL VERSUS HADORRA
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.47,0:02:07.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Hyunckel... you're alive?!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.56,0:02:08.85,Default,,0,0,0,,You...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.50,0:02:31.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Is this a dream? Or am I dead?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.60,0:02:34.38,Default,,0,0,0,,You're not dreaming. And you're not dead.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.42,0:02:36.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Hyunckel!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.72,0:02:37.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Maam.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.88,0:02:40.34,Default,,0,0,0,,You're alive! You...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.01,0:02:42.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank goodness!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.89,0:02:52.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, Hyunckel!\NI'm wounded over here! Help me out!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.16,0:02:54.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Have some medicinal herbs.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.98,0:02:59.90,Default,,0,0,0,,That bastard!\NWhat happened to equal treatment?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.32,0:03:02.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Explain this to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.67,0:03:06.91,Default,,0,0,0,,You were supposed to have died\Nwith the fall of the Underground Palace.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.91,0:03:09.41,Default,,0,0,0,,That's right. I should have.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.71,0:03:14.54,Default,,0,0,0,,But I was saved\Nat the brink of death by one man.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.42,0:03:18.17,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Truly, at the brink of death!{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.06,0:03:32.35,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}So you survived...{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.73,0:03:34.02,Default,,0,0,0,,...Crocodine.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.73,0:03:38.15,Default,,0,0,0,,My steel body is my one defining trait.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.15,0:03:41.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Plus your servants patched me up well.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.80,0:03:45.41,Default,,0,0,0,,I was barely alive\Nwhen this Garuda saved me.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.99,0:03:51.00,Default,,0,0,0,,I was the one who tried to kill you.\NWhy save me?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.00,0:03:55.19,Default,,0,0,0,,It was a warrior's mercy\Nthat you ordered my treatment.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.19,0:03:58.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Mercy must be repaid in kind.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.63,0:04:04.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Besides, you must continue\Nto help Dai and his friends from now on.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.84,0:04:09.83,Default,,0,0,0,,If mercy was your intent,\Nyou should have let me die.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.83,0:04:10.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Hm?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.56,0:04:13.25,Default,,0,0,0,,I ignored my own weakness
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.25,0:04:18.52,Default,,0,0,0,,and turned my hate to my master, Aban,\Nand towards humanity.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.90,0:04:21.99,Default,,0,0,0,,My death would have\Nat least made up for my crimes!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.61,0:04:26.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Now, I have to live on in my shame!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.49,0:04:29.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Hyunckel.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.70,0:04:36.12,Default,,0,0,0,,I believe the worth of a man lies in\Nhow much they can let go of the past.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.04,0:04:41.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Be it a life in shame, hated by all,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.48,0:04:45.34,Default,,0,0,0,,so long as you walk the path you believe,\Nisn't that enough?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.80,0:04:50.47,Default,,0,0,0,,The Garuda tells me Dai\Nand his friends have headed north.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.85,0:04:52.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Probably to Valge Island.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.27,0:04:55.45,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm going to go help them.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.45,0:05:00.96,Default,,0,0,0,,It's the least I can do after they\Nreminded me of a warrior's honor.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.96,0:05:02.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.65,0:05:10.16,Default,,0,0,0,,You're right. My crimes aren't so small\Nthat my death absolves them!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.16,0:05:15.91,Default,,0,0,0,,And you and Maam were the first people\Nto ever shed tears for me.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.91,0:05:20.90,Default,,0,0,0,,In order to repay those tears,\NI must... I must...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.90,0:05:23.84,Default,,0,0,0,,I must continue to fight!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.26,0:05:27.38,Default,,0,0,0,,What's that?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.55,0:05:31.37,Default,,0,0,0,,The Dark Armour Blade?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.37,0:05:35.93,Default,,0,0,0,,It was lost in the fall of\Nthe Underground Palace! How is it here?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.39,0:05:39.25,Default,,0,0,0,,And it's completely restored!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.25,0:05:42.61,Default,,0,0,0,,They say a true weapon\Nchooses its wielder.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.98,0:05:48.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Perhaps this Dark Blade was drawn here\Nby your renewed Aura.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.03,0:05:52.74,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}{\3c&H1717E4&}Amudo!{\i0}{\3c&H00000000&}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.51,0:06:06.80,Default,,0,0,0,,That's it!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.80,0:06:12.22,Default,,0,0,0,,So long as you have the will to fight,\Nthat armour shall never die!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.22,0:06:17.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you, Beast King!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.94,0:06:21.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Unbelievable!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.46,0:06:26.38,Default,,0,0,0,,I never trusted you, but for Crocodine\Nto betray us and join Dai!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.38,0:06:30.91,Default,,0,0,0,,You'll believe it when you hear him\Ndestroy the Dark Flame Spire.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.37,0:06:33.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Maam, can you stand?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.89,0:06:34.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.66,0:06:38.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Leave this to me.\NHead to Valge Tower with Popp.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.29,0:06:41.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Dai should be on his way there.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.42,0:06:43.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.17,0:06:48.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, okay then! Thanks!\NBest of luck to you!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.47,0:06:50.11,Default,,0,0,0,,What are you doing, Popp?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.11,0:06:53.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Forget him! He said go, so we're going!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.72,0:06:57.60,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Like I'll let him touch you\Na second longer!{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.82,0:07:09.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Traitors must die!\NThat's the law of the Dark Army!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.11,0:07:13.24,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll make your death slow and painful!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.24,0:07:16.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Now, how do you want to die?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.08,0:07:19.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Hadorra, are you looking down on me?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.64,0:07:23.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Or are you too stupid to tell\Nhow strong your opponents are?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.42,0:07:24.63,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.64,0:07:38.41,Default,,0,0,0,,These scrubs aren't worth my time!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.41,0:07:42.77,Default,,0,0,0,,If you want to kill me,\Ndo it by risking your own life!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.77,0:07:46.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Y-You brat!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.07,0:07:59.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't let him any closer\Nto the Dark Flame Spire!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.04,0:08:01.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Get back, old man!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.96,0:08:08.50,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}{\3c&H1717E4&}Beast King Anguish Blast!{\i0}{\3c&H00000000&}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.18,0:08:17.51,Default,,0,0,0,,No! The Dark Flame Spire!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.90,0:08:31.53,Default,,0,0,0,,I feel lighter! The Curse Field is gone!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.69,0:08:35.03,Default,,0,0,0,,What an astounding attack!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.16,0:08:40.91,Default,,0,0,0,,But "Anguish Blast"\Nsounds a little too ominous.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.37,0:08:44.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Why don't you call it,\N"Beast King Redemption Blast"?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.50,0:08:50.84,Default,,0,0,0,,That's not half bad! Thanks, old man!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.17,0:08:57.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, man. After all that trouble,\Nthere goes my Curse Field.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.36,0:09:00.06,Default,,0,0,0,,What is Master Hadorra doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.43,0:09:07.19,Default,,0,0,0,,The Dark Flame Spire has fallen.\NIt's your turn now.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.23,0:09:09.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Lord Hadorra!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.21,0:09:14.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Stay back, all of you!\NI'll show him my true power!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.44,0:09:18.47,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm no longer worthy\Nto call Aban, "Master."
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.47,0:09:21.79,Default,,0,0,0,,To claim to avenge my master\Nwould be impudent.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.79,0:09:26.83,Default,,0,0,0,,However, for taking the life\Nof my father, Bartos,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.08,0:09:29.42,Default,,0,0,0,,I cannot allow you to live!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.42,0:09:32.09,Default,,0,0,0,,You snotty whelp! Watch your tongue!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.09,0:09:35.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Like father, like son, you both defy me!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.17,0:09:38.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Begone!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.89,0:09:48.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Impossible! My Ionazun spell...?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.33,0:09:54.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Have you forgotten?\NMy armour repels all attack spells.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.69,0:09:57.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Prepare yourself, Hadorra!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.37,0:10:02.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Die!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.92,0:10:16.67,Default,,0,0,0,,There's nothing in this world\Nmy Hell's Claws can't penetrate!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.05,0:10:20.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Good! That's more like it!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.01,0:10:22.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Dai!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.76,0:10:25.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Popp! Maam!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.02,0:10:29.79,Default,,0,0,0,,It was Hyunckel! Hyunckel saved us!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.79,0:10:31.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Talk about an oasis in a desert!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.98,0:10:36.53,Default,,0,0,0,,That's great! So Hyunckel\Nis a Disciple of Aban after all!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.90,0:10:40.11,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sure Master Aban must be proud.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.82,0:10:43.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's go! To save Leona!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.93,0:10:44.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Right!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.29,0:10:48.96,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Be careful, Hyunckel.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.13,0:10:59.80,Default,,0,0,0,,They're evenly matched!\NNo, Lord Hadorra seems at a disadvantage!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.72,0:11:08.43,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}He's not the Dark Commander for nothing!\NHe has the power to back it!{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.43,0:11:13.71,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}He's stronger than I imagined!\NNo wonder Dark King Ban likes him!{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.71,0:11:17.15,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}And without my spells,\NI'm at a disadvantage!{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.65,0:11:19.86,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}If I can do something about that armour...{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.86,0:11:24.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I see...{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.91,0:11:27.87,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}He's coming for the final showdown!{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.62,0:11:31.25,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}{\3c&H1717E4&}Bloody Sukuraido!{\i0}{\3c&H00000000&}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.17,0:11:42.30,Default,,0,0,0,,That was rather disappointing.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.30,0:11:44.64,Default,,0,0,0,,It's over, Hadorra.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.64,0:11:45.86,Default,,0,0,0,,No!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.86,0:11:48.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Lord Hadorra lost?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.52,0:12:01.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Impossible! How can you move\Nwith your vitals pierced?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.65,0:12:05.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Unfortunately for you, I have a heart\Non both sides of my chest.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.28,0:12:09.24,Default,,0,0,0,,I was waiting for you to lower your sword!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.24,0:12:14.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Now let me fill your armour\Nwith my flames of hell!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.50,0:12:17.71,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}{\3c&H1717E4&}Merazoma!{\i0}{\3c&H00000000&}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.14,0:12:30.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Hyunckel...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.98,0:12:37.56,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}{\3c&H1717E4&}BLOODY SUKURAIDO!{\i0}{\3c&H00000000&}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.98,0:12:42.57,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}{\3c&H1717E4&}FIVE FINGER FLARES{\i0}{\3c&H00000000&}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.28,0:12:49.72,Default,,0,0,0,,How do you like my flames?\NAgonizing, aren't they?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.72,0:12:53.46,Default,,0,0,0,,They won't go out\Nuntil your body is burned away!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.75,0:12:57.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Curse you and your dirty tricks!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.55,0:13:06.51,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I can't... I can't move my body!{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.51,0:13:09.49,Default,,0,0,0,,So much for your mighty sword.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.49,0:13:13.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Meanwhile, I still have my secret weapon!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.14,0:13:19.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Now watch as I unleash the full power\Nof my greatest spell!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.31,0:13:23.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Can your punctured armour withstand it?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.57,0:13:25.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Take this!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.13,0:13:27.32,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}{\3c&H1717E4&}Begiragon!{\i0}{\3c&H00000000&}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.17,0:13:45.63,Default,,0,0,0,,I've won!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.05,0:13:50.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Stubborn little brat! He's finally dead!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.35,0:13:53.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Lord Hadorra has won!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.20,0:13:54.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Lord Hadorra, are you hurt?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.99,0:13:58.52,Default,,0,0,0,,It's nothing.\NI merely lost one of my hearts.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.06,0:14:01.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Is this all that survived?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.92,0:14:02.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, Lord!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.73,0:14:07.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Good! We're going after Dai\Nand we'll slaughter them all!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.03,0:14:07.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, Lord!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.41,0:14:14.55,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}No! Dai and the others are in danger!{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.55,0:14:16.72,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I have to stop them!{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.72,0:14:20.71,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}But I don't have any way to fight!{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.50,0:14:25.27,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}What can I do? What weapon can I use?!{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.27,0:14:26.55,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Life itself.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.47,0:14:29.38,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Aban?!{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.22,0:14:33.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Life energy. Basically, your Aura.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.48,0:14:42.27,Default,,0,0,0,,What is this attack?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.57,0:14:45.36,Default,,0,0,0,,I just focused my Aura.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.28,0:14:49.26,Default,,0,0,0,,As a Warrior, you cannot cast spells.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.26,0:14:54.99,Default,,0,0,0,,If your sword is lost,\Nthe only weapon left is life itself.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.41,0:14:58.79,Default,,0,0,0,,In such a situation, use your life energy.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.12,0:15:01.43,Default,,0,0,0,,In other words, you fight with your Aura.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.43,0:15:02.73,Default,,0,0,0,,My Aura...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.73,0:15:09.30,Default,,0,0,0,,But an Aura is offensive life energy.\NIt's very, very difficult to control.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.30,0:15:15.14,Default,,0,0,0,,If your heart is full of malice,\Nit can put your own life at risk.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.72,0:15:20.45,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't need such a skill.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.45,0:15:24.52,Default,,0,0,0,,All I have to do is defeat my enemy\Nwith my sword, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.19,0:15:29.78,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Back then, I laughed at Aban's teachings.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.28,0:15:32.74,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}But now, I understand.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.03,0:15:36.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Now I know I can do it!{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.08,0:15:40.81,Default,,0,0,0,,It's almost impressive how stubborn\Nthe Students of Aban can be.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.81,0:15:42.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait a minute, Lord Hadorra!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.17,0:15:46.79,Default,,0,0,0,,We can take a half-dead enemy like him!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.01,0:15:52.76,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Huh? Has he given up?{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.18,0:16:03.48,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}What is that? An extreme amount of energy\Nis gathering at Hyunckel's forehead!{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.06,0:16:06.27,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Wait, is this... his Aura?!{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.27,0:16:11.99,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}If it means stopping Hadorra here,\Nthen I'll gladly use all of my life!{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.32,0:16:19.95,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Aban, my master! Give this ungrateful\Nstudent his final strength!{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.95,0:16:22.75,Default,,0,0,0,,N-No! Get away!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.75,0:16:25.38,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}{\3c&H1717E4&}Grand Cross!{\i0}{\3c&H00000000&}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.88,0:16:37.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Dai, that light!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.20,0:16:38.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.28,0:16:39.76,Default,,0,0,0,,What is it, you two?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.97,0:16:43.69,Default,,0,0,0,,It's just like back then.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.44,0:16:49.15,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}The light from when Master Aban\Nfought Hadorra and died!{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.44,0:16:53.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Megante!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.16,0:17:05.12,Default,,0,0,0,,It was just like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.67,0:17:09.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Like the final flash of life itself.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.44,0:17:10.75,Default,,0,0,0,,No...!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.80,0:17:15.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey! Where are you going, Dai?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.40,0:17:18.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Where do you think?! To go help Hyunckel!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.51,0:17:23.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Hold on!\NWe don't know if that was him or not!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.12,0:17:29.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Besides, he can't use spells!\NHe can't cast Megante and die!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.19,0:17:34.15,Default,,0,0,0,,But that's no ordinary light!\NWin or lose, he won't be alright!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.53,0:17:36.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Isn't that right, Maam?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.26,0:17:39.57,Default,,0,0,0,,What are you thinking?!\NWhat about Princess Leona?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.57,0:17:41.59,Default,,0,0,0,,There's still time until sundown!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.59,0:17:44.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Stop it! There's nothing you can do now!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.29,0:17:47.10,Default,,0,0,0,,No! At the very least, I have to go!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.10,0:17:48.37,Default,,0,0,0,,You can't, Dai!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.67,0:17:53.42,Default,,0,0,0,,We're going to Valge Tower! We have to!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.42,0:17:55.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Why?! Are you abandoning Hyunckel?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.92,0:17:59.05,Default,,0,0,0,,That's what he wants!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.55,0:18:05.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Hyunckel and Crocodine\Ncame here to help us.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.89,0:18:09.65,Default,,0,0,0,,It's all so you can save Princess Leona!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.77,0:18:15.36,Default,,0,0,0,,If you turn back now, all they've done,\Ntheir very lives will be for nothing!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.61,0:18:21.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Besides, Hyunckel is a Disciple of Aban.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.24,0:18:27.14,Default,,0,0,0,,He'd risk his life to save his friends\Nno matter what!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.14,0:18:29.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Just as our Master did!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.92,0:18:37.44,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}They're strong... They're so strong,\Nboth Hyunckel and Maam.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.44,0:18:38.67,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I can't compete...{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.34,0:18:40.84,Default,,0,0,0,,All right, Maam.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.30,0:18:45.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Right now, our purpose is\Nto save Leona as soon as possible!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.60,0:18:48.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's go! The tower is right there!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.98,0:18:56.63,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Hyunckel, Crocodine, thank you!\NI promise I'll save Leona!{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.63,0:19:00.49,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}So please, please don't die out there!{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.62,0:19:10.96,Default,,0,0,0,,I somehow managed to withstand it.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.96,0:19:14.00,Default,,0,0,0,,How lucky I had these minions\Nto use as shields.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.05,0:19:23.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Is this the power\Nof that Grand Cross attack?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.89,0:19:26.64,Default,,0,0,0,,What terrifying power!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.94,0:19:33.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Hyunckel!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.99,0:19:42.49,Default,,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.87,0:19:48.87,Default,,0,0,0,,I get it now!\NGrand Cross was an incomplete attack!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.87,0:19:54.21,Default,,0,0,0,,As a result, it drew upon\Nall the Aura Hyunckel had!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.54,0:19:59.30,Default,,0,0,0,,All that's remains is this soulless husk!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.38,0:20:08.06,Default,,0,0,0,,After all your trouble, it looks like\NI get the last laugh, Hyunckel!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.02,0:20:14.83,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll just cleave your head off,\Nand massacre Dai and his friends,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.83,0:20:18.90,Default,,0,0,0,,and there'll be no one left in my way!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.69,0:20:22.82,Default,,0,0,0,,You can grind your teeth in the afterlife!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.82,0:20:28.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Along with Aban, Bartos,\Nand your friends that follow you!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.49,0:20:31.62,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Aban...{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.54,0:20:33.79,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Bartos...{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.38,0:20:37.38,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Master!{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.54,0:20:39.92,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Dad!{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.85,0:20:51.47,Default,,0,0,0,,This is the end! Die, Hyunckel!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.27,0:20:59.13,Default,,0,0,0,,I-Impossible!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.13,0:21:03.65,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}He had spent all of his Aura completely!{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.49,0:21:15.79,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Even unconscious, he still retains\Nthe last of his will to fight!{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.46,0:21:20.34,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Well done, Hyunckel.\NYou are indeed, a true...{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.34,0:21:22.46,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}warrior...!{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.81,0:21:41.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Man, Master Hadorra is useless!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.19,0:21:44.74,Default,,0,0,0,,He can't even beat a few brats...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.49,0:21:49.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh well. I guess this means\NDai's head will be worth even more!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.32,0:21:54.06,Default,,0,0,0,,The Hero's Party that the Dark Army\Nworking together couldn't beat.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.06,0:21:59.08,Default,,0,0,0,,If I obliterate them,\Nthe more glory for me!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.23,0:22:25.99,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Kindness is the magic of kind people{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.23,0:22:25.99,On Top,,0,0,0,,{\i1}yasashisa wa yasashii hito ga tsukaeru mahou{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.15,0:22:32.99,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Then do I have no choice\NBut to just be a normal person?{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.15,0:22:32.99,On Top,,0,0,0,,{\i1}jaa boku wa tada no hito de iru shikanaino?{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:33.16,0:22:36.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I'm not sure{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:33.16,0:22:36.20,On Top,,0,0,0,,{\i1}doudarou{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.50,0:22:44.17,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Even if the place I call home may change{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.50,0:22:44.17,On Top,,0,0,0,,{\i1}kaeru basho wa ne kawatte yuku kedo{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:44.34,0:22:46.71,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Listen to me, Mother{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:44.34,0:22:46.71,On Top,,0,0,0,,{\i1}naa kaasan boku wa{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.88,0:22:52.85,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I will never change those I protect{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.88,0:22:52.85,On Top,,0,0,0,,{\i1}mamoru hito wo kaetari shinai{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:53.30,0:22:57.52,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I wonder what you'd say{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:53.30,0:22:57.52,On Top,,0,0,0,,{\i1}anata wa nannte iukana{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.68,0:23:01.73,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}At times I can be cowardly and small{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.68,0:23:01.73,On Top,,0,0,0,,{\i1}tokiyori yowaki de chippoke de{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:01.90,0:23:08.19,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}What would you say to me\NAs I hesitate to even hesitate?{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:01.90,0:23:08.19,On Top,,0,0,0,,{\i1}mayou koto ni mo mayou boku ni nannte iukana{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:08.36,0:23:14.03,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Unlike the today that I sought{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:08.36,0:23:14.03,On Top,,0,0,0,,{\i1}sagashite ita kyou to chigatte{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:14.20,0:23:19.33,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I'm sure you'd laugh at my disappointment{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:14.20,0:23:19.33,On Top,,0,0,0,,{\i1}ochikonnde shimau boku wo warau no darou{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.43,0:23:39.89,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Saved by Hyunckel and Crocodine,\NDai's party reaches Valge Tower at last.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:40.02,0:23:45.52,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}But again, they are at the mercy\Nof Flazzard's powerful attack.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:45.69,0:23:51.95,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}When all hope seems lost, Dai\Nremembers the words of his master, Aban!{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:52.61,0:23:55.66,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Next time on{\i}\NDRAGON QUEST The Adventure of Dai{\i1},{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:55.83,0:23:58.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}"The Final Aban Style Technique"{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:58.20,0:24:00.16,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}The adventure continues!{\i}
